t of touch with reality. </span></span>But I am making a broader, more unexpected claim, too: <span class="Underline"><span style="text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">the U</span></span>nited <span class="Underline"><span style="text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">S</span></span>tates <span class="Underline"><span style="text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">is </span></span>only <span class="Underline"><span style="text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">at the beginning of its power.</span> **<span style="text-decoration: none;">The twenty first century will be the American century</span>**</span>. 

